{
  "chapter": 25,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十五回 花海迷魂\n\n胡铁花与琵琶公主讨论楚留香和姬冰雁的危险，决定前往救援。他们乘坐鬼船抵达沙漠深处的石峰群，被白衣人曲无容押送进入秘谷鬼径。楚留香试图用美男计，曲无容揭露自己被毁容的面容。一点红安慰曲无容。途中遇到被奴役的扫地奴隶，楚留香感慨石观音的魔力。进入花海后，花香使众人昏迷。楚留香醒来发现曲无容痴痴望着一点红，黄衣少女和绛衣少女出现，对楚留香调情。楚留香试图套取迷药信息，但两少女不肯透露。本章展现了沙漠深处的神秘与危险，以及角色间微妙的情感变化。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "若是承认混蛋就有酒喝，我每天承认一次也没关系。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "text": "我已改变主意，酒不能给你喝了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "你……你主意不嫌改变得太快了么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "text": "这些东西全是老臭虫的，是不是?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "睡鞋和肚兜却是死公鸡的，你可千万别吃醋，你一吃醋，我就没得喝了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "text": "我不是这意思……你想，这些东西老臭虫始终都带在身上，但现在却将之深深埋在地下……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "那只因他已易容改扮，若将这些东西藏在身上，怕泄漏了身份。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "text": "但你再想想，这些东西藏在他身上，别人又怎会发觉呢?除非他明知此行有被别人抓住的危险。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "不错，我果然不能再喝酒了，若非他们明知此行十分凶险，死公鸡绝不会将这些见不得人的贴身之物拿出来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "女人果然比男人细心，这么重要的问题，我竟会没有想到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "text": "这也不是女人比男人细心，只不过因为女人对她所喜欢的人，总是特别关心而已。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "这就是极乐之星，你快送回去吧!",
      "tone": "激动",
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "text": "你呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "我一定得要先去找老臭虫。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "text": "但你已答应过王妃将此物送回去。",
      "tone": "提醒",
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "不错，我还答应了她许多事，但我既已知道老臭虫和死公鸡有了危险，天大的事，都只好先放在一边。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "text": "你我既已知道他有危险，我难道还能放心走开么?",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "你也要跟我去?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "那么……这极乐之星呢?",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "text": "你自己说过，天大的事都可先放在一边的，是么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "不行，我不能带你去。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "此行既然十分凶险，你却是个娇滴滴的大姑娘，万一有什么……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "text": "你莫忘了，这里是沙漠，在这里我比你要有用得多，何况，就算你真不带我去，我还是要跟着你的。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "text": "没有女人，冷冷清清，有了女人，鸡犬不宁，这话可真是一点也不错。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "好险恶的所在，这里只怕就是石观音的根据地了。",
      "tone": "沉思",
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "text": "你们两条腿还能动么?",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "text": "你们两条腿若还能动，就下去吧!",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "text": "你可是想我挖出你的眼睛来么?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "姑娘方才是为了要让别人认为姑娘就是石夫人，所以才蒙起脸来，但在下等既已知道姑娘并非石夫人，姑娘为何还不……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "text": "你可是想瞧瞧我的脸?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "久闻石夫人门下俱是国色天香，姑娘若肯让在下一睹风采，在下虽死，也算对得住自己的这双眼睛了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "text": "原来他又想用'美男计'了，但你无论怎么样花言巧语，她难道还会放了你不成?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "text": "国色天香……好，我就让你瞧瞧我的国色天香。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "text": "现在你瞧见了么?你的眼福可真不浅，以后你也一定要记住，曲无容乃是世上最丑的女人，再没有别人比得上。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "容貌美丑，只在人们一念之中，姑娘若非绝代风华，容貌又怎会被人所毁，姑娘既然本是风华绝代，形貌被毁又有何妨……只因别人纵能毁得姑娘的形貌，但姑娘的风骨自在，却是谁也毁不去的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "text": "下去，下去……这里不是你多话的地方。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "text": "你不丑，你很美。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "text": "你……你说什么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "大汉",
      "text": "是否此刻就扎起他们的眼睛来?",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "text": "用不着费事，这秘谷鬼径，我就算再带他们走几次，他们也无法辨出方向的……普天之下，无论谁到了这里，也休想自己走得出去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "真的么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "text": "你要想出去，除非被抬出去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "好险恶的地势，其实石夫人本用不着再费这么多心力，摆下这阵式的。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "text": "这里已算险恶了么?……真正险恶的地方，还没有到哩!",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "在哪里?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "朋友，你为何不坐下来歇息歇息?",
      "tone": "关心",
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "text": "不歇息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "朋友，你难道喜欢扫地么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "text": "喜欢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "但这里地上的沙子，是永远也扫不完的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "text": "我扫的不是沙子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "是什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "text": "是死人的骨头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "但这里并没有死人的骨头。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "text": "现在虽没有，立刻就会有的。",
      "tone": "威胁",
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "想不到荒漠之中，竟有这样的花海。",
      "tone": "惊叹",
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "text": "此花本非凡俗之人所能梦想。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "这花种难道是来自天上的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "text": "正是来自天上的。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "如此说来，咱们的眼福倒真不浅了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "姑娘方才说真正凶险处还未到，现在只怕已到了吧?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "text": "你认为这里很凶险?",
      "tone": "反问",
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "特别美丽的事物中，往往都隐藏着凶险，特别甜蜜的香气中，往往都有毒……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "text": "原来他也并非我想像中那么高明。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣少女",
      "text": "这就是传说中那英俊的强盗，最潇洒的流氓么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "绛衣少女",
      "text": "传说中只怕将他说得太厉害了，他若真有那么厉害，此刻怎会躺在这里?",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣少女",
      "text": "但他看来却比传说中还更迷人，难怪有许多女孩子生怕他不去偷自己家里的东西，为的只不过是想见他一面而已。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣少女",
      "text": "丑丫头，知道自己被人喜欢，就故意做出这副假道学的样子……哼!你看不惯我们，我们还看不惯你哩!",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "姑娘说话最好小声些，莫要被她听见了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣少女",
      "text": "听见了又怎样?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "以在下看来，那位曲姑娘似乎是这里的大人物，两位姑娘看来都入门不久，若是得罪了她，岂非大是不便?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣少女",
      "text": "你用不着替我们担心，师傅对徒弟倒全都一视同仁，我们不怕她。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "绛衣少女",
      "text": "只要你对我们好，我们也一样有法子可以让你在这里过得舒服些的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "绛衣少女",
      "text": "你叹什么气?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "只可惜在下全身一丝气力也没有，否则……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "绛衣少女",
      "text": "你不用着急，总有一天……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "你难道不着急么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "绛衣少女",
      "text": "你呀……果然名不虚传，是个又可恶、又可爱的风流贼。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "我真不懂自己中的究竟是什么迷药，怎地如此厉害?",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "两位姑娘想必也不会知道那是什么迷药的，我方才本该问问那位姑娘才是。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "绛衣少女",
      "text": "你以为只有她知道?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "姑娘们难道也知道么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣少女",
      "text": "你可瞧见那些花么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "text": "在下若是没有瞧见，此刻又怎会变成如此模样?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    }
